    "Name": "Demolisher Squad",
    "Content": "[[Image]]Demlisher Squad.png|2 Demolishers popping out of an ARC[[/Image]]\nDemolisher squads are [[0b10]] aligned [[Squad|squads]] that are dispatched to eliminate large groups of hostiles, especially [[Assembled]]. They are sent to the general area of a lot of hostiles, where they will roam around looking for bots to fight. They consist of a single [[C-30 ARC]] containing 2 [[Demolisher|Demolishers]]. Demolisher squads will never exit the map under normal circumstances after being dispatched.\nAn alert will indicate whenever a Demolisher squad is dispatched. Additionally, the log will display a message like [[GameText]]ALERT: Infestation in the Mines, dispatching Demolisher response squad.[[/GameText]] Depending on the method triggering the squad, a different reason may be given in the alert.\n[[Heading]]How to get Demolisher Squads[[/Heading]]\n[[List]]Assembled infestation: Any Assembled infestation events will trigger an immediate Demolisher response|[[Spoiler]]Friendly Assembled: If Cogmind has used a [[Core Reset Matrix]] and uses a [[Mobile Assembly Unit]] to create allied Assembled, Demolishers will be sent after a random amount of turns[[/Spoiler]]|Too many allies: If Cogmind has 18 or more allies, Demolishers may be dispatched to Cogmind's current location.[[/List]]"
